<p>in My Liferay Spring MVC, new lines on Text Area is not working.Where on Plain Spring mvc it is working.</p>  <p>Plain Spring MVC:                    Text area tage is -> <code>&lt;form:textarea path="theTextArea"/&gt;</code>                    User input as(<strong>with out bullet</strong>) three new lines</p>  <ul> <li>aaa</li> <li>bbb</li> <li>ccc</li> </ul>  <p>On Submit at server side when I inspect the bean the                              <strong>theTextArea = aaa\r\nbbb\r\nccc</strong> and same will be save on db. and on my view page I am using <code>&lt;pre&gt;&lt;c:out value="${theBean.theTextArea}"&gt;&lt;/c:out&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</code> And getting perfect three new lines view on page.</p>  <p>But on same it is not working on Liferay Spring MVC portlet. New line is converting to <strong>blank space</strong></p>  <ul> <li>aaa  </li> <li>bbb</li> <li>ccc</li> </ul>  <p>is converting to <strong>aaa bbb ccc</strong></p>  <p>Not sure how to handle on liferay.</p>